data.description:
New to market, 186 Covert Street is a captivating 3-Family house with 3,600 SQ of space in desirable and thriving Bushwick! This one-of-a-kind 7-bedroom, 5 full-bathroom home offers a harmonious blend of contemporary comfort and timeless allure, appealing to buyers seeking a spacious, multi-generational living space. 
Step into the tastefully designed owners duplex, enhanced with ADA approval for easy accessibility; it features 3 bedrooms and a renovated bathroom on the garden level, plus a full, finished basement with an additional full bathroom. The primary suite offers a luxurious retreat with sliding doors that lead to the private backyard. 
The upper level boasts a beautifully renovated 1-bedroom, 1-bathroom apartment with a new kitchen, a walk-in closet, and plenty of storage. The deck, accessed through the kitchen, adds to the charm and convenience. On the top floor, youll find a delightful 2-bedroom unit with 2 full bathrooms, and a brand-new kitchen, attracting potential tenants or homeowners with its abundance of natural light and stylish finishes. 
This property is impeccably maintained, with a roof that's less than a year old, a newer deck, and many other updates. All windows are in pristine condition, and the installed security cameras provide added peace of mind. Ideally situated near Irving Square Park, this home immerses you in Bushwicks vibrant community, with charming shops, eateries, and easy access to public transportation including the L, J, and Z train lines just a few blocks away. 
Dont miss this exceptional opportunity, contact us now for a viewing!
